                "caption": "Figure 2:SimCoderturns a user prompt into an interactive environment through an automatic self-evolving loop: it writes tools, creates reusable skills, reuses them across iterations, and refines the scene with verifier feedback. NavMesh-based tools are used to generate solvable navigation tasks.SimCoderfurthers uses embodied-agent feedback to autonomously adapt environment difficulty and co-evolve with the embodied agent (purple loop).",
